BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Tech Lancaster
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/tech-lancaster-meetups/
UID:event_313118796@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260324T024416Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260326T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260326T203000
SUMMARY:Tech Lancaster Meetup
DESCRIPTION:Tech Lancaster Meetups\nWe will be upstairs in "The Sanctuary"
  - when you walk in the main entrance just head up the stairs! We will hav
 e signs as you walk in to guide you.\nPizza is provided free upstairs. Bee
 r/wine/soda/etc at the bar downstairs!\n\nImportant update!\nThe patio out
  front in being remodelled\, so you will need to use the rear entrance. Se
 e this video if you would like to see what it looks like in advance: https
 ://www.instagram.com/reels/DWCIvIxjuUn/\n\nThis months speakers:\n**Zach F
 edor - MacGyvered Microphones**\nExploring the science of sound as I scrap
  together some studio equipment with little more than some magnets and a s
 tick of gum.\n\n**Tyler Golden - Fun with Sensors: Tracking Beers Poured o
 n St. Patrick's Day**\nTyler will present his latest iteration of a yearly
  hobby project - tracking drafts poured at the local pub on St. Patrick's 
 Day. Using inexpensive sensors and microcontroller boards\, he’ll demons
 trate how to measure the amounts being poured\, stream the data in real ti
 me\, and visualize the flow on a public dashboard.\n\nTypical schedule of 
 events:\n\n6:30 PM Doors Open/Pizza/Mingle\n\n7:00 PM Introduction/Announc
 ements\n\n7:05 PM First Speaker\n\n7:35 PM Break\n\n7:45 PM Speaker 2\n\n8
 :15 PM End
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/tech-lancaster-meetups/events/3131187
 96/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260129T214346Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260129T214346Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
